---
title: Sunny California-Style Chorizo Rice Bowl  with Guacamole-Ranch Dressing
description: This is everything you love about a California-style chorizo sammie but in salad form! This dish is chock full of juicy tomatoes, crisp lettuce,  spiced chorizo and sharp cheddar, and it's finished off with a drizzle of guacamole dressing.
